# Visual / UX Direction

Full product direction: **`.cursor/rules/messenger-inspired-direction.mdc`**

## Quick Reference

- **Product name in-world:** HVAC Technician World (repo: hvac-tech-vision-lab)
- **Feel:** compact browser-native service-call diorama — not training module, not open world
- **Controls:** click/tap to move and inspect; keyboard optional accessibility only
- **Copy tone:** service call / field technician — avoid school-quiz and “WebGL training POC” framing in user-facing text
- **Messenger:** quality benchmark only — never copy assets, story, or branding

## Interaction Loop

Point → move → arrive → face → inspect/scan → diagnose. Inspect ≠ Scan. No early answer leakage.

## Scope

One polished Mission 1 neighborhood scene before expansion. No Mission 2, backend, external models, or 2D curriculum coupling in polish passes.
